txt.en: 'Wha... pa, pay... goblins! You vile worm!'
'I will hear no more insults from you, Dwarf!'
'You dwarves have no right here, go back you your mountain!'
'And you've no right to block our way, Elf!'
'Driving the wolves and sickle-flies to our lands is one thing, but paying goblins to harry us is repugnant!'
